WEBVTT

00:00:01.817 --> 00:00:05.253
haynt iz yanuar der fuftseter, nayntsn

00:00:05.260 --> 00:00:06.840
nayntsik zibn.

00:00:07.133 --> 00:00:10.215
di ibergelebte iz Mindl Melamed,

00:00:10.626 --> 00:00:12.847
un der TAPE iz numer dray.

00:00:14.676 --> 00:00:16.323
ir hot zikh opgeshtelt oyf dem

00:00:16.971 --> 00:00:20.711
az ir zayt g- ir hot gelebt in Popovets in dem,

00:00:21.038 --> 00:00:23.158
in dem lager iz geven a geto,

00:00:23.535 --> 00:00:25.199
hot ir gelebt biz...

00:00:24.953 --> 00:00:27.350
bizn fir un fertsikstn yor.

00:00:25.729 --> 00:00:27.157
fir un fertsiktn yor.

00:00:29.965 --> 00:00:31.444
vos iz forgekumen vayter?

00:00:32.310 --> 00:00:36.710
in fir un fertsikstn yor, ven s'hot zikh geendikt di milkhome...

00:00:38.149 --> 00:00:39.915
di milkhome hot zikh nit geendikt nokh.

00:00:39.580 --> 00:00:41.940
ikh veys, di milkhome iz nokh geven.

00:00:41.997 --> 00:00:45.568
nu, m'iz geven in fir un fertsikstn yor ⟨m-⟩ dortn in lager

00:00:45.574 --> 00:00:50.900
di gantse tsayt. m'hot zikh gut ongemutshet un THAT'S ALL. vos kon ikh nokh fun dort dertseyln?

00:00:51.177 --> 00:00:54.630
kent ir dertseyln vi s'iz forgekumen di bafrayung ayere fun dem...?

00:00:53.978 --> 00:00:56.540
di bafrayung? m'hot zikh aleyn bafrayt.

00:00:56.540 --> 00:00:59.591
m'hot gehert az s'hot zikh geko- -FINISHt di milkhome,

00:01:00.205 --> 00:01:02.949
un m'hot ongehoybn, di rusn, kumen

00:01:03.630 --> 00:01:05.429
noent tsun undz,

00:01:06.583 --> 00:01:09.077
un m'iz durkhgegan undzer shtetele,

00:01:09.077 --> 00:01:10.630
durkhgegan rusn,

00:01:10.630 --> 00:01:13.684
un azoy vi di mame hot gehert az s'hot zikh bafrayt,

00:01:13.684 --> 00:01:16.095
iz men nokh... m'iz geven narish,

00:01:16.573 --> 00:01:22.746
un zi iz shoyn nokhgegangen, vi azoy zey zenen gegan, di, di rusn, azoy ⟨i-⟩ di yidn, ile yidn.

00:01:22.746 --> 00:01:24.954
yeder hot gedenkt, er geyt aheym.

00:01:25.551 --> 00:01:29.038
er geyt aheym. m'hot gemeynt az m'hot nokh epes in der heym.

00:01:29.787 --> 00:01:31.401
m'iz gegangen aheym

00:01:31.508 --> 00:01:33.580
al- ale tsu fus.

00:01:33.580 --> 00:01:37.149
m'hot in ergets nisht gehat zikh vu oyftsuzetsn oyf aheymtsuforn.

00:01:37.149 --> 00:01:39.585
m'iz gegan fun eyn dorf tsum andern

00:01:39.625 --> 00:01:42.910
un m'hot ibergenekhtikt; di goyim hobn undz arayngenemen.

00:01:42.910 --> 00:01:45.740
di Ukrayner goyim hobn gelitn a sakh.

00:01:45.740 --> 00:01:47.544
zey hobn zeyer mitgefilt

00:01:47.544 --> 00:01:50.100
a oremen, a hungerikn.

00:01:50.100 --> 00:01:51.771
zey flegn undz araynnemen.

00:01:51.771 --> 00:01:54.235
zey hobn undz geleygt shlofn in di sarayen,

00:01:54.235 --> 00:01:57.573
vu dos ferd iz geshlofn, di ku iz geshtanen dortn.

00:01:58.373 --> 00:02:04.374
esn hot men undz arayngebrakht. m'hot nokh mitgegibn a broyt oyfn veg tsu geyn vayter aheym.

00:02:05.427 --> 00:02:09.504
mir zenen gegan oyf di vegn biz mir ze'mir gekumen tsu undzer shtetl.

00:02:10.472 --> 00:02:12.570
gekumen tsun undzer shtot,

00:02:12.570 --> 00:02:15.464
opgebrent geven dos gantse shtetl,

00:02:15.464 --> 00:02:19.760
in der mit; di yidishe shtiber zenen geven in gantsn farbrent.

00:02:19.939 --> 00:02:25.909
zeyer veynik mentshn zenen aheymgekumen fun undzer shtetl, vayl undzer shtetl hobn a sakh mentshn

00:02:25.909 --> 00:02:27.610
farloyrn oyf di vegn.

00:02:29.119 --> 00:02:31.914
un in dem lager in Popovets,

00:02:31.971 --> 00:02:36.470
fun hunger un fun kelt dortn iz men oysgesh- oysgeshtorbn gevorn.

00:02:37.287 --> 00:02:41.640
un s'iz aheymgekumen efsher tsvontsik FAMILIES fun undzer shtot.

00:02:42.298 --> 00:02:47.620
un mir ze'mir gekumen. s'iz gesht- geshtanen eyn shtibl. s'iz geven

00:02:47.620 --> 00:02:50.139
noent tsu di goyim, mayn zeydn's,

00:02:50.213 --> 00:02:53.947
di vos mayn mame hot gegibn a nadn der shvester.

00:02:53.947 --> 00:02:57.581
on tirn, on fentster; nor di vent zenen geven.

00:02:58.937 --> 00:03:02.730
di mame hot genemen a tir un hot tsugeshtelt dort,

00:03:03.055 --> 00:03:04.258
un m'iz,

00:03:04.258 --> 00:03:07.900
m'hot gedarft vintern in der sh- tsebrokhener shtub.

00:03:08.488 --> 00:03:12.460
den hot zikh dervust a krist fun lebn undzer shtot,

00:03:12.471 --> 00:03:15.780
vos er iz geven mayn tatn's a guter-bruder,

00:03:16.167 --> 00:03:19.620
az Zeydl beker's vayb mit di kinder zenen do.

00:03:21.195 --> 00:03:23.349
iz er gekumen in shtot arayn,

00:03:23.895 --> 00:03:28.650
un er hot gefregt oyfn ba- oyf dem bazar, vu di vayber hobn dort farkoy⟨ft,⟩

00:03:28.650 --> 00:03:30.030
vu se voynt

00:03:30.375 --> 00:03:31.990
Zeydl's vayb.

00:03:32.535 --> 00:03:36.275
hot men im gezogt vu. er iz tsugekumen tsun undz.

00:03:37.142 --> 00:03:40.376
er hot zikh zeyer derfreyt mit mayn mamen, davke a goy,

00:03:40.922 --> 00:03:44.520
un er hot gezogt azoy: "Roze, se geyt vinter.

00:03:44.520 --> 00:03:46.159
di shtub iz tsebrokhn.

00:03:46.159 --> 00:03:48.054
host nit mit vos tsu heytsn.

00:03:48.550 --> 00:03:51.213
ikh'l dikh araynnemen tsu mir in dorf arayn

00:03:51.213 --> 00:03:52.700
oyfn vinter.

00:03:52.735 --> 00:03:55.446
iz vinter ibervinter UNK bay mir,

00:03:55.823 --> 00:03:59.107
un zumer," zogt er, "vestu zen vos du host tsu tun."

00:03:59.518 --> 00:04:02.840
mayn mame hot gekont a bisl neyen. zi iz geven a meydl,

00:04:02.840 --> 00:04:05.370
hot zi geneyt shnayderay ergets.

00:04:05.458 --> 00:04:08.020
zogt er, "du vest UNK fardinen oyfn dorf,

00:04:08.020 --> 00:04:09.975
un di kinder veln zayn bay mir."

00:04:10.099 --> 00:04:12.711
er hot gehat a shtibl, a zumer-shtibl,

00:04:12.711 --> 00:04:15.830
vos zey flegn zumer kokhn in droysn dort.

00:04:16.089 --> 00:04:19.639
hot er dos shtibl bavornt gut, se zol zayn varem,

00:04:19.639 --> 00:04:23.790
ongebrakht a fule kamer mit heytsung.

00:04:23.830 --> 00:04:28.726
zogt er, "ot hostu holts. ven s'vet oysgeyn," zogt er, "ikh'l forn in dorf, in vald arayn

00:04:28.726 --> 00:04:30.900
un dir onhakn, ikh'l dir brengen.

00:04:31.193 --> 00:04:32.807
gey un arbet!"

00:04:33.640 --> 00:04:36.232
hot arayngegibn shoyn tsu zaynem a khaver.

00:04:36.323 --> 00:04:39.270
dort iz geven a mashin. di mame hot zikh

00:04:39.580 --> 00:04:41.801
oy-, ayngearbet dort,

00:04:41.875 --> 00:04:49.681
un me fleg ir araynbrengen, zi hot oyfgeneyt. m'hot ir gegibn a bisl boyml, m'hot ir gegibn a bisl mel. m'hot gedarft dem vinter durkhpraven.

00:04:50.025 --> 00:04:55.216
mir ho'mir durkhgepravet dort dem vinter. zumer iz di mame aroysgeforn keyn Lipkan

00:04:55.982 --> 00:04:58.493
un hot zikh dort oysgekukt. zogt zi,

00:04:58.493 --> 00:05:00.570
"voynen ho'mir nisht vu.

00:05:00.808 --> 00:05:03.620
lomir zikh araynforn keyn Tshernevits,

00:05:04.065 --> 00:05:05.814
un mir vel'mir zen

00:05:06.107 --> 00:05:07.366
vos tsu ton."

00:05:07.812 --> 00:05:11.500
zi kumt arayn keyn Tshernevits. keyn gelt ho'mir nisht.

00:05:11.575 --> 00:05:14.086
undz hot zi nokh gelozt in dorf baym goy

00:05:14.086 --> 00:05:15.854
un zi iz aleyn geforn.

00:05:16.958 --> 00:05:21.764
keyn gelt iz nisht geven. mir ho'mir gornisht gehat: naket un borves,

00:05:21.764 --> 00:05:24.930
nor vos m'hot gehat dos bisl esn vos zi hot fardint.

00:05:25.716 --> 00:05:28.325
arayngekumen keyn Tshernevits,

00:05:28.872 --> 00:05:31.346
un hot zikh bagegnt mit mentshn.

00:05:31.707 --> 00:05:33.692
hot men ir gezogt azoy:...

00:05:33.934 --> 00:05:36.341
ven mir ze'mir nokh geven in Lipkan,

00:05:37.613 --> 00:05:43.074
un mir ze'mir gezesn bay mayn zeydn's shtub in droysn... dos iz shoyn geven varem,

00:05:44.413 --> 00:05:47.500
ven m'iz krikgekumen funem dorf, funem goy...

00:05:47.755 --> 00:05:51.100
hot men gekhapt a yunger-man, di rusn,

00:05:51.180 --> 00:05:53.016
hobn gekhapt a yunger-man,

00:05:53.016 --> 00:05:54.970
vos er hot gehandlt,

00:05:55.399 --> 00:05:58.810
un er hot getrogn in gartl dos gelt,

00:05:58.810 --> 00:06:00.710
vayl er hot keynem nit gehat.

00:06:00.710 --> 00:06:03.808
er fleg nem- koyfn VOENNe shikh,

00:06:03.808 --> 00:06:07.579
nemen bay di banen, baytn, ikh veys dort vos er hot geton,

00:06:07.579 --> 00:06:09.500
un er hot gemakht dos gelt.

00:06:10.266 --> 00:06:13.351
un mir zits'mir in droysn, ikh mit mayn bruderl

00:06:13.351 --> 00:06:14.832
un nokh a meydele,

00:06:14.991 --> 00:06:18.073
zitsn in droysn, un do firt im

00:06:18.096 --> 00:06:19.777
tsvey militsyonern

00:06:19.800 --> 00:06:21.245
in polits arayn.

00:06:22.180 --> 00:06:25.498
hot er geklert, er vet aropvarfn dem gartl,

00:06:26.027 --> 00:06:29.227
vayl er hot dort gehat a tsvey goldene tsenerlekh oykh;

00:06:29.976 --> 00:06:32.957
mir zits'mir dokh dort, vel'mir es geyn oyfheybn,

00:06:32.963 --> 00:06:37.074
un oyb m'vet im oplozn, vet er kumen tsun undz, er zol es opnemen.

00:06:37.502 --> 00:06:39.000
dos gedenk ikh.

00:06:40.287 --> 00:06:46.230
az im hot gefirt di polits, zenen zey dokh geven shtark klug; er iz gegan fun hintn un zey fun fornt.

00:06:46.260 --> 00:06:49.345
hot er geton a shpilye oyf dem gartl, un in groz

00:06:49.345 --> 00:06:51.016
hot er im gegibn a varf arayn,

00:06:51.016 --> 00:06:53.612
az mir zol'mir zen; er hot gekukt tsun undz.

00:06:54.124 --> 00:06:56.767
abi zey zenen aroyfgegan a bisl hekher,

00:06:56.875 --> 00:07:01.273
bin ikh gelofn, un tu a khap dem gartl, un nem arayn in shtub arayn.

00:07:02.612 --> 00:07:07.360
nem arayn dem gartl in shtub arayn, iz shoyn mayn mame geven in der heym funem dorf.

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:08.799
s'iz geven fraytik.

00:07:10.206 --> 00:07:17.658
un breng arayn dem gart-... zogt di mame, "vos iz dos?" zog ikh, "m'hot gefirt a yunger-man, di, tsvey militsyonern hobn gefirt UNK..."

00:07:17.833 --> 00:07:22.771
hot zi shoyn genemen dem gartl un zi hot im farbahaltn. zi hot afile nisht gekukt vos s'iz dortn do.

00:07:23.098 --> 00:07:28.030
zi hot im farbahaltn. zogt zi, "efsher vet got helfn, er vet krikkumen un lozn zikh im opnemen."

00:07:28.030 --> 00:07:31.988
m'hot zikh gemutshet oyfn toyt. ven s'iz a andere oyf mayn mame's plats,

00:07:31.988 --> 00:07:33.723
git zi es im nisht,

00:07:34.810 --> 00:07:42.465
nor mayn mame hot dokh geklert, "efsher in dem zkhus veln mayne kinder zayn gezunt. zey hobn ibergelebt di milkhome; in dem zkhus efsher..."

00:07:42.640 --> 00:07:45.120
zi hot gegleybt in di zakhn.

00:07:46.183 --> 00:07:53.754
kumt krik der yunger-man; m'hot im opgelozt. m'hot bay im tsugenemen di BOCANCn vos er hot dort getrogn oyf tsu farkoyfn un m'hot im opgelozt.

00:07:53.878 --> 00:07:56.319
er kumt arayn tsun undz in shtub arayn

00:07:56.376 --> 00:07:59.762
un khapt arum mayn mamen, nemt dem baytl, un trogt im.

00:08:00.223 --> 00:08:02.039
un khapt arum mayn mamen.

00:08:02.181 --> 00:08:05.212
er vil ir gibn fuftsik rubl, zogt zi, "neyn.

00:08:05.556 --> 00:08:08.390
in dem zkhus veln mayne kinder zayn gezunt,

00:08:08.390 --> 00:08:10.252
un ikh'l zey konen vayter..."

00:08:10.252 --> 00:08:13.619
un hot nisht gevolt nemen di fuftsik rubl. hot zikh gemutshet oyfn toyt

00:08:13.619 --> 00:08:15.710
un nisht genemen di fuftsik rubl.

00:08:15.833 --> 00:08:20.889
un den, dernokh, in a tsvey tog arum, iz di mame arayngeforn keyn Tshernevits.

00:08:21.283 --> 00:08:28.415
arayngeforn keyn Tshernevits, un hot zikh arumgedreyt, un hot nisht gehat vu arayntsugeyn az zi zol konen arbetn.

00:08:29.198 --> 00:08:34.687
iz zi arayngegan tsun a DOMOUPRAV... ir veyst s'heyst a DOMOUPRAV? a balebos iber di gasn,

00:08:34.687 --> 00:08:36.278
iber di shtiber.

00:08:36.522 --> 00:08:37.950
a DOMOUPRAV...

00:08:37.950 --> 00:08:39.738
un hot im gezogt azoy:

00:08:40.302 --> 00:08:46.740
"ikh hob nisht vu zikh ahintsutun. ikh bin geblibn mit di kinder. mayn man hot men geshosn.

00:08:47.136 --> 00:08:50.560
un tu-... ir zent dokh a yid. tut mir a toyve,

00:08:50.899 --> 00:08:53.200
zet mir ergets an arbet."

00:08:53.278 --> 00:08:56.240
hot er gezogt, er hot a arbet far ir:

00:08:56.502 --> 00:08:58.791
⟨zi⟩ zol arayngeyn kern di gasn,

00:08:59.556 --> 00:09:01.630
vet men ir gibn a shtub.

00:09:01.783 --> 00:09:03.481
hot zi gezogt, "gut."

00:09:04.450 --> 00:09:06.722
mayn mame iz gevorn a dvornitshke

00:09:06.964 --> 00:09:08.730
un hot gekert di gasn,

00:09:08.938 --> 00:09:12.087
un hot undz ibergenemen keyn Tshernevits.

00:09:13.495 --> 00:09:16.037
ibergenemen undz keyn Tshernevits.

00:09:16.060 --> 00:09:19.423
den iz geblibn mayn tatn's shvester lebn

00:09:19.423 --> 00:09:20.629
in Rusland.

00:09:20.629 --> 00:09:24.052
mayn onkl iz geven natshalnik ZHELEZNODOROGe.

00:09:24.666 --> 00:09:26.490
zenen zey geblibn lebn,

00:09:26.455 --> 00:09:27.849
fun der ayzerban?

00:09:26.490 --> 00:09:27.832
un zey hobn...

00:09:27.855 --> 00:09:28.910
ha?

00:09:28.227 --> 00:09:29.486
ayznban?

00:09:29.374 --> 00:09:30.296
yo.

00:09:31.770 --> 00:09:33.789
er iz nokh do; er iz in Yisroel.

00:09:35.027 --> 00:09:36.607
un zi hot zikh dervust

00:09:36.816 --> 00:09:38.690
az mir leb'mir,

00:09:38.959 --> 00:09:41.500
az di mame iz do mit dray kinder.

00:09:41.524 --> 00:09:43.560
abi zi hot zikh dos dervust,

00:09:43.566 --> 00:09:45.098
iz zi aropgekumen

00:09:45.098 --> 00:09:48.690
fun Rusland. zi iz geven ergets in Sibir, zenen zey geven.

00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:50.819
iz zi gekumen tsu forn

00:09:50.819 --> 00:09:54.500
un hot shoyn tsugenemen bay mayn mamen di eltere shvester.

00:09:54.500 --> 00:10:00.070
zogt zi, "abi s'zol dir zayn gringer mit di tsvey kinder, lomikh hobn di lebn mir."

00:10:00.070 --> 00:10:02.080
vayl zi hot keyn kinder nit gehat.

00:10:02.398 --> 00:10:07.387
zi hot genemen mayn shvester un zey zenen ibergekumen keyn KISHINЁV voynen.

00:10:08.288 --> 00:10:13.850
ibergekumen voynen keyn KISHINЁV. mayn shvester hot dort gelernt, gevorn a BUKHGALTER.

00:10:14.413 --> 00:10:17.180
un zi hot, zi hot ir khasene gemakht.

00:10:17.704 --> 00:10:21.360
hot ir khasene gemakht, iz zi gekumen tsu forn tsu der mamen.

00:10:21.360 --> 00:10:23.789
vu voynen hot zi bay der TЁTye nit gehat;

00:10:24.100 --> 00:10:27.756
zi iz gezesn in eyn ROOM mit a shutfesdiker kikh.

00:10:28.487 --> 00:10:31.050
iz zi gekumen voynen tsu der mamen.

00:10:33.027 --> 00:10:37.560
ikh bin geven, bin arayngegan arbetn in der ershter ⟨SHVEYNer fabrik⟩.

00:10:37.937 --> 00:10:40.715
mayn bruderl iz gegan in der yidisher shkole arayn.

00:10:41.481 --> 00:10:45.002
a por shtivelekh iz er gegan ongeton mit drot farbunen.

00:10:45.497 --> 00:10:47.516
azoy raykh ze'mir geven.

00:10:48.417 --> 00:10:50.820
mayn mame hot zikh gemutshet oyfn toyt.

00:10:51.285 --> 00:10:55.070
gearbet dvornikeray tsulib dem, zi zol hobn di shtub.

00:10:55.740 --> 00:10:59.126
fleg aroysgeyn, f⟨leg zi⟩ neyen a por kufaykes

00:10:59.503 --> 00:11:03.597
un aroystrogn, farkoyfn, vayl s'hot nit gestayet, m'hot nit gehat vos tsu esn.

00:11:03.739 --> 00:11:05.680
m'hot zikh gut ongemutshet.

00:11:06.574 --> 00:11:08.373
vos zol ikh aykh nokh dertseyln?

00:11:09.038 --> 00:11:10.490
vos zol ikh aykh zogn?

00:11:10.590 --> 00:11:11.681
nu,

00:11:10.658 --> 00:11:13.841
vi azoy may- azoy mayn mame hot zikh gemutshet?

00:11:11.772 --> 00:11:13.929
vi hot ir zikh bakant mit ayer

00:11:13.881 --> 00:11:18.110
mayn man iz gekum- mayn man iz geven a shtikl, soykher.

00:11:13.929 --> 00:11:15.411
kumedikn man?

00:11:19.348 --> 00:11:22.008
er hot gehandlt mit m- SHVEYNe mashinen.

00:11:22.335 --> 00:11:24.843
gekumen tsu forn keyn Tshernevits,

00:11:25.322 --> 00:11:27.594
tsu zayn khaver's a shviger,

00:11:27.938 --> 00:11:29.889
un dort iz er ayngeshtanen.

00:11:30.132 --> 00:11:32.539
mayn shvester hot gehat a BABele.

00:11:34.030 --> 00:11:36.504
iz zi gelign in der heym in kimpet.

00:11:37.978 --> 00:11:43.726
un er iz geven bay der baleboste. zogt er ir, "ikh volt gevolt, ir zolt mir redn epes a meydl."

00:11:45.167 --> 00:11:47.500
zogt zi, "ikh hob a meydl far dir.

00:11:48.002 --> 00:11:54.000
az du vilst zi zen," zogt zi, "shtey do mit mir in droysn. in der fri geyt zi tsu der arbet,

00:11:54.000 --> 00:11:55.490
vel ikh zi dir vayzn."

00:11:56.423 --> 00:11:58.526
ikh bin gegan mit mayn khavertorin.

00:11:59.089 --> 00:12:01.296
zi vayzt mikh un zi.

00:12:01.296 --> 00:12:03.980
zogt er, "ot di," zogt er, "vil ikh."

00:12:04.320 --> 00:12:06.410
ikh bin gegan tsu der arbet.

00:12:07.071 --> 00:12:13.123
di baleboste zayne iz aruntergegan tsu mayn mamen; zi iz geven a bisl fun undzer mishpokhe.

00:12:13.602 --> 00:12:16.532
aruntergekumen tsu mayn mamen, zogt zi, "Rosye,

00:12:16.605 --> 00:12:19.197
ikh hob a yunger-man far Mile's vegn,

00:12:19.812 --> 00:12:21.880
zeyer a vazhner bokher.

00:12:21.880 --> 00:12:23.020
er handlt.

00:12:23.020 --> 00:12:28.040
er iz a raykher." er iz geven raykh. er iz geven a shpekulant, iz er geven raykh.

00:12:29.734 --> 00:12:32.470
"loz Mile tsukumen tsu mir."

00:12:32.569 --> 00:12:34.858
zogt zi, "mayn Mile vet nit geyn.

00:12:35.758 --> 00:12:38.200
zi," zogt zi, "vet nisht geyn," zogt zi.

00:12:38.200 --> 00:12:41.088
zogt zi, "veys vos? shik zi, zi zol nemen a klizme.

00:12:41.088 --> 00:12:42.470
Lide ligt dokh;

00:12:42.470 --> 00:12:43.754
zi hot gehat di BABY.

00:12:43.754 --> 00:12:45.523
me darf ir makhn a klizme."

00:12:45.732 --> 00:12:48.133
oysgeklert, di vayber klern oys!

00:12:48.133 --> 00:12:50.231
ir veyst vos heyst a klizme UNK...?

00:12:51.098 --> 00:12:53.460
ikh kum aheym fun der arbet.

00:12:53.494 --> 00:12:56.800
zogt mayn mame, "Mile, tu a gey tsu tsu Golden,

00:12:56.987 --> 00:12:59.245
un loz zi dir layen di klizme,

00:12:59.245 --> 00:13:03.260
vayl Lide iz shoyn dray tog nit ofn geven; zi ligt in kimpet."

00:13:03.923 --> 00:13:07.840
zog, zog ikh, "OKAY." vos zol ikh geyn zogn der mamen az neyn?

00:13:07.840 --> 00:13:10.965
ikh gey tsu ahin, iz er do mitn shutef,

00:13:10.965 --> 00:13:13.620
un me shteyt un me pakevet mashinen

00:13:13.677 --> 00:13:15.763
avektsushikn keyn Libevne,

00:13:16.208 --> 00:13:17.754
fun zayn shtetl.

00:13:18.722 --> 00:13:24.040
kum arayn, ikh zog der Golden. di Golde git es mir, in a setke arayngeleygt.

00:13:24.679 --> 00:13:31.946
un den zogt zi, "Mile, baken dikh mit, dos iz Fanye's a FRIEND, un dem," mitn shutef, mikh bakent.

00:13:31.969 --> 00:13:34.477
zey hobn gehat tsvey biletn tsu geyn

00:13:34.534 --> 00:13:36.660
tsu ⟨"Koldunyen"⟩,

00:13:37.032 --> 00:13:40.198
in teater arayn, in yidishn teater tsu geyn.

00:13:40.795 --> 00:13:48.470
zogt der shutef, toret im shoyn unter, "nem mayn bilet un nem zi mit." ikh bin im zeyer gefeln gevorn, dem shutef oykh.

00:13:49.333 --> 00:13:57.342
tut er a makh... er hot zikh mit mir bakent, er firt mikh aroys. zogt er, "ir volt gevolt efsher geyn haynt in ovnt mit mir in teater arayn?"

00:13:57.535 --> 00:14:00.800
s'hot mir epes nisht gepast im optsuzogn.

00:14:00.927 --> 00:14:04.660
zog ikh, "SURE," zog ikh, "gut," un gey.

00:14:05.061 --> 00:14:08.784
er hot mikh mitgenemen in teater arayn, hot mikh opgefirt aheym.

00:14:09.347 --> 00:14:12.050
un ven er hot mikh opgefirt, zogt er,

00:14:12.098 --> 00:14:14.893
"ikh volt gevolt zikh mit aykh nokh a mol bagegenen."

00:14:15.912 --> 00:14:18.859
zog ikh, "ven ir vet kumen dos tsveyte mol"...

00:14:18.932 --> 00:14:20.861
der shtrik iz mir geven

00:14:20.861 --> 00:14:22.149
baym haldz:

00:14:22.307 --> 00:14:25.288
esn iz nit geven vos, gemutshet hot men zikh.

00:14:25.800 --> 00:14:31.540
mayn shvester iz geven mitn man, mit a pitsele kind, mayn mame mitn bruderl, un ikh,

00:14:31.540 --> 00:14:32.696
ile in eyn ROOM.

00:14:32.770 --> 00:14:34.721
der tsveyter lager iz geven.

00:14:36.398 --> 00:14:40.087
zog ikh, "az ir vet krikkumen, veln mir zen vos s'vet zayn.

00:14:41.258 --> 00:14:44.180
efsher," zog ikh, "vet zayn yo merer vi neyn."

00:14:44.180 --> 00:14:47.040
⟨z-⟩ kh'bin geven yung UNK ⟨m'hot zikh⟩...

00:14:47.147 --> 00:14:50.350
er iz avekgeforn, hot ongemakht a rash in shtetl

00:14:50.350 --> 00:14:53.317
az er kumt dos tsveyte mol mit a vaybl.

00:14:57.120 --> 00:14:59.324
er iz gekumen s'tsveyte mol.

00:15:00.985 --> 00:15:06.610
zenen mir avekgegan mitvokh, in a mitvokh. m'hot zikh farshribn in ZAGS.

00:15:07.296 --> 00:15:09.510
shabes hot men khasene gehat,

00:15:09.510 --> 00:15:13.297
un zuntik hot er mikh avekgenemen keyn Poyln tsu zikh in shtetl arayn.

00:15:13.557 --> 00:15:17.061
bay zey in shtetl iz geven a POGRANICHNe zone:

00:15:17.100 --> 00:15:19.389
ahin hot men nisht gekont araynforn.

00:15:19.547 --> 00:15:22.713
bay zey in shtetl in zibn un fertsikstn yor

00:15:22.753 --> 00:15:24.885
hobn zey keyn hunger nisht gelitn,

00:15:24.885 --> 00:15:27.472
un mir ho'mir gelitn a groysn hunger.

00:15:27.850 --> 00:15:31.002
in zibn un fertsikstn yor iz geven aza hunger:

00:15:31.002 --> 00:15:32.770
der tsveyter lager.

00:15:33.334 --> 00:15:35.440
nisht geven gornisht vos tsu esn,

00:15:35.440 --> 00:15:38.340
nisht geven afile far gelt vu tsu koyfn,

00:15:38.565 --> 00:15:40.398
aza hunger iz geven.

00:15:40.742 --> 00:15:45.670
er hot mikh arayngebrakht tsu zikh in shtub arayn. ikh tu a kuk: se shteyen bay ⟨i⟩m

00:15:45.670 --> 00:15:47.317
tsvey zek mit mel.

00:15:47.577 --> 00:15:49.480
bin ⟨i⟩kh geven yung.

00:15:51.508 --> 00:15:53.640
hob ikh geton a farknet

00:15:53.719 --> 00:15:55.600
un opgebakn broyt,

00:15:55.795 --> 00:15:59.130
az ikh hob gekont esn broyt vifl kh'hob gevolt.

00:15:59.473 --> 00:16:03.031
hob ikh bay nakht, ⟨a SU-⟩ fir un tsvontsik sho hob ikh geesn,

00:16:03.031 --> 00:16:05.087
hob oyfgeesn a gebekl broyt.

00:16:05.194 --> 00:16:07.837
in dray monatn bin ikh gevorn azoy o,

00:16:09.008 --> 00:16:11.418
vos kh'hob mikh nit gekont onesn,

00:16:11.418 --> 00:16:13.440
azoy hungerik bin ikh geven.

00:16:13.750 --> 00:16:18.390
mir hobn gevoynt dortn nisht lang, a zeks, zibn monatn.

00:16:18.424 --> 00:16:20.270
ikh bin krank gevorn.

00:16:20.449 --> 00:16:22.440
er hot dort keynem nit.

00:16:22.440 --> 00:16:26.108
zog ikh, "kuk, ikh hob a mamen un a shvester un a bruderl,

00:16:26.108 --> 00:16:28.138
un du bist eyner aleyn do.

00:16:28.228 --> 00:16:30.739
lomir iberforn keyn Tshernevits."

00:16:30.739 --> 00:16:33.318
dos iz geven punkt far der reforme,

00:16:33.561 --> 00:16:35.910
vos m'hot gedarft baytn dos gelt.

00:16:36.244 --> 00:16:38.820
hob ikh mikh ongekhapt, me zol iberforn.

00:16:39.147 --> 00:16:44.625
m'iz ibergeforn keyn Tshernevits. s'iz gevorn di reforme. fun zayn gelt iz gornit gevorn.

00:16:45.458 --> 00:16:47.477
er iz arayngegan arbetn,

00:16:48.411 --> 00:16:50.350
un ikh hob nisht gearbet.

00:16:50.350 --> 00:16:55.374
er iz arayngegan arbetn. friert hot er gearbet bay seltser ongisn sifonen,

00:16:55.583 --> 00:17:02.700
un biz er hot zikh ibergevarfn in a kleyt arayn tsu arbetn, a kleyn kleytele. a kleyn kleytele, hob ikh im shoyn geholfn.

00:17:04.054 --> 00:17:07.510
un azoy ho'mir gefirt dos lebn biz haynt tsu tog,

00:17:07.782 --> 00:17:10.189
di gantse tsayt in eynem geven.

00:17:10.820 --> 00:17:14.900
ikh hob im geholfn tsu der arbet, biz got hot geholfn,

00:17:14.900 --> 00:17:17.260
s'hot zikh im opgezukht a bruder.

00:17:18.194 --> 00:17:20.010
er hot gedarft papirn,

00:17:21.064 --> 00:17:23.640
a metrike, a pasport tsu makhn,

00:17:24.185 --> 00:17:26.672
hot er geshribn in SEL'SOVET arayn,

00:17:26.672 --> 00:17:29.799
un in SEL'SOVET hot gearbet zayner a khaver.

00:17:30.514 --> 00:17:36.465
hot er shoyn gegibn undz a telegrame keyn Tshernevits az "dayn bruder iz geblibn lebn: Hershl iz do."

00:17:37.602 --> 00:17:45.270
un er hot undz shoyn gegibn di telegrame, ho'mir gehat zayn adres shoyn, un m'hot shoyn gegibn tsun im a telegrame, tsum bruder tsu zaynem,

00:17:45.617 --> 00:17:49.998
un m'hot zikh ongehoybn ibershraybn, un den der bruder iz gekumen tsun undz.

00:17:50.393 --> 00:17:53.070
un der eltster bruder iz geforn glaykh

00:17:53.110 --> 00:17:55.044
fun Rusland keyn Poyln.

00:17:55.776 --> 00:18:01.260
avekgeforn keyn Poyln. in Poyln hot er undz geshikt papirn. er hot undz, er hot zikh oykh dervust

00:18:01.260 --> 00:18:04.511
fun undz. er hot geshribn a briv in SEL'SOVET arayn

00:18:04.534 --> 00:18:07.987
un er hot gefregt tsi s'iz emetser do fun zayn familye.

00:18:08.483 --> 00:18:10.990
hot geentfert zayner a FRIEND

00:18:11.048 --> 00:18:12.307
im teykef...

00:18:12.820 --> 00:18:15.193
NO, er hot gegibn undz a telegrame

00:18:15.283 --> 00:18:17.000
az Kalmen lebt,

00:18:17.000 --> 00:18:20.115
er iz do in Poyln, un shoyn undz gegibn dem adres,

00:18:20.115 --> 00:18:21.639
oyf der telegrame,

00:18:21.696 --> 00:18:26.398
un mir ho'mir shoyn gegibn a telegrame keyn Poyln, un er hot zikh dervust fun undz.

00:18:26.657 --> 00:18:31.340
er iz in Poyln nisht lang geven, zenen zey ibergeforn keyn Yisroel.

00:18:31.720 --> 00:18:35.840
mir ho'mir shoyn ayngegibn papirn keyn Poyln, oder m'hot undz opgezogt.

00:18:35.989 --> 00:18:39.344
dernokh ho'mir ayngegibn, er hot undz ⟨ge⟩shikt a vize fun Yisroel.

00:18:39.344 --> 00:18:41.200
hot men undz oykh opgezogt.

00:18:41.200 --> 00:18:44.438
un den iz er fun Yisroel ibergeforn keyn Amerike,

00:18:44.460 --> 00:18:49.950
hot undz geshikt a vize. demlt hot men undz erloybt tsu forn keyn Yisro- keyn Amerike.

00:18:50.434 --> 00:18:54.430
zenen mir gekumen ater, hot er undz oykhet zeyer geholfn.

00:18:54.430 --> 00:18:56.430
in der ⟨BEGIN⟩ hot er undz geholfn,

00:18:56.560 --> 00:19:00.199
oder ikh bin teykef arayngegan arbetn. tsu di akht tog

00:19:00.610 --> 00:19:03.490
bin ikh arayngegan in a fabrik arayn arbetn.

00:19:03.563 --> 00:19:07.944
un in der fabrik hob ikh opgearbet eyn un tsvontsik yor,

00:19:08.372 --> 00:19:10.036
mit di balebatim.

00:19:10.178 --> 00:19:12.267
m'hot fun mir zeyer gehaltn.

00:19:12.267 --> 00:19:13.946
kh'hob gearbet bay leder,

00:19:13.946 --> 00:19:17.540
kh'hob gearbet bay shmates; vos m'hot gedarft, hot men mir gegibn,

00:19:17.540 --> 00:19:19.230
un ikh hob gemakht.

00:19:20.252 --> 00:19:24.988
un den bin ikh krank gevorn. m'hot mir gedarft operirn oyfn harts.

00:19:25.365 --> 00:19:28.498
m'hot mir arayngeshtelt dray PACEMAKERS...

00:19:28.993 --> 00:19:31.079
 dray, PACEMAKE-

00:19:31.778 --> 00:19:37.000
.. azoy, azoy zogt men? ikh gedenk nit v⟨UNK⟩...

00:19:37.060 --> 00:19:41.620
un dernokh hot men mir arayngeshtelt tsum yor a PACEMAKER.

00:19:43.118 --> 00:19:47.426
un azoy bin ikh geblibn zitsn oyf pensye, un bin a pensyonerte gevorn.

00:19:47.426 --> 00:19:49.440
nu, vos vilt ir nokh?

00:19:48.045 --> 00:19:51.532
zogt mir, in Tshernevits, az ir hot gelebt, iz dortn gevezn a

00:19:49.963 --> 00:19:50.963
yo.

00:19:51.640 --> 00:19:54.553
kultur yidisher lebn, a RELIGЁ-...?

00:19:53.412 --> 00:19:57.080
s'iz geven. s'iz geven der yidisher teater,

00:19:57.512 --> 00:20:00.240
s'iz geven vu zikh tsunoyftsukumen.

00:20:00.853 --> 00:20:02.838
me fleg zikh tsunoyfkumen,

00:20:02.895 --> 00:20:06.123
fleg zingen, tantsn. s'iz shoyn geven a radyo.

00:20:06.123 --> 00:20:09.930
m'hot zikh ENJOYet. m'hot nit shlekht in Tshernevits gelebt.

00:20:11.029 --> 00:20:16.794
Tshernevits iz shoyn geven a lebn a bisl. oder baym rus, dos lebn iz geven zeyer ayngeshtelt.

00:20:16.935 --> 00:20:20.405
mayn man hot gedarft arayn oyf tsen yor in tyurme arayn,

00:20:20.462 --> 00:20:22.730
un ikh hob im aroysgeshlept.

00:20:23.280 --> 00:20:26.430
un den hob ikh gezen az me darf fun dort antloyfn,

00:20:27.432 --> 00:20:30.227
un ayngegibn keyn Amerike, un m'iz avekgeforn.

00:20:30.503 --> 00:20:33.551
di tokhter di groyse hot gelernt in KISHINЁV.

00:20:35.430 --> 00:20:41.279
hot zi gelernt. dort hot zi geFINISHt, bay mayn TЁTyen vos hot zi gehaltn, hot zi geFINISHt oyf a NURSE.

00:20:41.488 --> 00:20:44.877
un ven m'hot gedarft forn, farn forn, iz zi aheymgekumen,

00:20:44.877 --> 00:20:47.760
un zi iz aroysgeforn fun dortn a NURSE.

00:20:47.783 --> 00:20:50.325
di kleyne tokhter iz geven in z-

00:20:50.415 --> 00:20:52.721
in zibetn, akhtn klas,

00:20:52.727 --> 00:20:54.375
zibetn klas.

00:20:55.090 --> 00:21:01.786
zi iz gekumen ater, iz zi teykef arayngegan in shkOOL arayn. zi fleg aheymkumen un veynen: "mame, ikh zits vi a ber.

00:21:01.786 --> 00:21:04.669
ikh veys nit vos me redt. ikh veys nit vos me tut."

00:21:04.911 --> 00:21:09.900
s'hot gedirt a dray monatn. mayne kinder zenen bay tog un bay nakht nisht geshlofn.

00:21:10.243 --> 00:21:14.030
kh'fleg zey koyfn hundert apelsinkelekh, hundert marantselekh.

00:21:14.030 --> 00:21:17.091
iber nakht hobn zey zey oyfgegesn. zey flegn nemen piln,

00:21:17.091 --> 00:21:21.099
az zey zoln nit shlofn, az zey zoln konen lernen dos englishe.

00:21:21.099 --> 00:21:24.845
nokh dray monatn hobn mayne beyde kinder geredt english

00:21:24.845 --> 00:21:26.269
vi do geboyrn.

00:21:26.477 --> 00:21:30.140
in shkOOL hot men shoyn mayn tokhter gegibn di Amerikaner kinder,

00:21:30.140 --> 00:21:32.158
zi zol zey unterhelfn,

00:21:32.316 --> 00:21:35.584
un mit eyn klas hot men zi ibergehekhert hekher,

00:21:35.623 --> 00:21:39.410
vayl zi hot shtark gut gelernt. abi zi hot gekhapt dos loshn,

00:21:39.410 --> 00:21:42.497
"iz dos, mame, vos ikh lern in fiftn klas,

00:21:42.497 --> 00:21:44.933
iz lernt men do in akhtn klas.

00:21:45.192 --> 00:21:48.116
azoy o," zogt zi, "zolst dikh far mir nit zorgn."

00:21:48.116 --> 00:21:50.298
zi hot geFINISHt a kaledzh,

00:21:50.389 --> 00:21:52.003
a tseyn-TEKHNIK.

00:21:52.870 --> 00:21:54.850
zi hot khasene gehat.

00:21:54.979 --> 00:21:57.555
der man hot zi nit gelozt geyn arbetn.

00:21:57.763 --> 00:22:00.004
er hot gehat a GAS STATION,

00:22:00.004 --> 00:22:03.731
hot er gezogt, "du zay mit mir." er hot moyre gehat, m'vet zi im oyskhapn.

00:22:04.328 --> 00:22:06.617
zi iz geven zeyer a sheyn meydele.

00:22:07.213 --> 00:22:09.160
un zeyer voyle kinder,

00:22:09.272 --> 00:22:11.054
beyde tsvey tekhter.

00:22:11.854 --> 00:22:15.420
zey hobn gute kinder, un zey zenen geven gut.

00:22:15.420 --> 00:22:17.160
zey zenen haynt tsu tog

00:22:17.338 --> 00:22:18.986
gut tsu undz,

00:22:19.026 --> 00:22:20.457
lib undz.

00:22:20.457 --> 00:22:23.171
me kumt tsun undz, mir gey'mir tsu zey.

00:22:23.380 --> 00:22:25.950
me veys nisht vos tsu tun mit undz.

00:22:25.950 --> 00:22:27.747
ikh bin gelign in HOSPITAL,

00:22:27.747 --> 00:22:29.451
mayn tokhter hot nisht gearbet

00:22:29.451 --> 00:22:31.392
un iz geshlofn mit mayn man do,

00:22:31.392 --> 00:22:34.781
az zi zol gants fri konen zayn lebn mir in HOSPITAL.

00:22:36.019 --> 00:22:41.362
azoy az oyf mayne kinder zhaleve ikh mikh nit. got zol mir helfn, zoln mir nor zayn gezunt.

00:22:41.340 --> 00:22:43.336
 vos iz forgekumen mit ayer muter?

00:22:43.596 --> 00:22:46.650
mit mayn mamen? mayn mame iz do geshtorbn.

00:22:46.752 --> 00:22:49.598
mayn mame iz geven in Tshernevits,

00:22:50.582 --> 00:22:52.516
geblibn in Tshernevits,

00:22:52.692 --> 00:22:56.040
un ven mir ze'mir avekgeforn hot zi khasene gehat.

00:22:57.012 --> 00:22:58.339
hot khasene gehat

00:22:58.480 --> 00:23:02.760
⟨fa⟩r a Lipkaner yunger-man vos er hot gevust vemen er nemt.

00:23:02.867 --> 00:23:06.270
un mir, ikh hob zey aroysgenemen ater.

00:23:06.664 --> 00:23:11.267
zey aroysgenemen ater. ven zey kenen nit, me zol zey geven helfn,

00:23:11.267 --> 00:23:13.846
gibn, vet er zi nisht geven genemen,

00:23:13.920 --> 00:23:16.420
nor azoy vi kh'hob oysgefunen

00:23:16.420 --> 00:23:17.576
az zi vet kumen,

00:23:17.582 --> 00:23:19.469
un zi vet zikh voynen bazunder,

00:23:19.469 --> 00:23:21.401
vet men ir gibn oyf tsu lebn,

00:23:21.401 --> 00:23:23.448
hob ikh z⟨ey⟩ aroysgenemen ater.

00:23:23.455 --> 00:23:27.077
un dernokh hot mayn mame aroysgenemen mayn bruder ater.

00:23:27.403 --> 00:23:29.624
di mame hot im shoyn aroysgenemen,

00:23:29.884 --> 00:23:34.434
vayl zi iz a Ukrayner, di shvegerin mayne, un zi hot nisht gevolt forn.

00:23:35.385 --> 00:23:40.947
mit groyse tsores hot zi im aroysgenemen ater. zi hot gezogt, ir kadesh muz zi hobn do.

00:23:40.988 --> 00:23:43.660
zi hot nisht gevust az zi vet im bagrobn.

00:23:44.768 --> 00:23:49.820
er hot bakumen a harts-atake bay zibn un fertsik yor un er iz geshtorbn.

00:23:50.792 --> 00:23:55.747
zogt mir, ir halt oyf di yidishe yontoyvim? shabes...?

00:23:54.302 --> 00:23:56.320
voden? voden?

00:23:55.973 --> 00:23:57.680
ir bentsht likht?

00:23:56.698 --> 00:23:59.024
voden? ikh fleg bentshn,

00:23:59.024 --> 00:24:01.417
oder do, di letste tsayt, epes...

00:24:01.710 --> 00:24:05.380
hob ikh ⟨es⟩ avekgeshtelt. s'shteyt der laykhter in shafe ineveynik.

00:24:05.380 --> 00:24:10.850
oder unter di yontoyvim tsinen mir on likht, me shtelt oyfn tish, farshpreyt dos tish.

00:24:10.907 --> 00:24:13.190
mir haltn fun di yontoyvim.

00:24:13.253 --> 00:24:15.830
fun ile yontoyvim di yidishe haltn mir.

00:24:16.341 --> 00:24:21.583
zogt mir, nokh dem vos ir hot azoy fil ibergelebt in ayer lebn, farlorn azelkhe,

00:24:21.589 --> 00:24:24.333
azoy fil, noente mentshn,

00:24:21.966 --> 00:24:23.720
azoy fil...

00:24:24.492 --> 00:24:26.696
vos volt ir veln zogn tsum ende

00:24:26.871 --> 00:24:28.603
fun ayer intervyu

00:24:28.626 --> 00:24:30.175
vos zol ikh aykh zogn?

00:24:28.693 --> 00:24:29.986
vos ir git undz?

00:24:30.175 --> 00:24:32.890
az dos shenste un dos beste ho'mir farloyrn?

00:24:33.334 --> 00:24:37.783
ven mayn foter zol geven lebn, vet undz gornit geven gefelt nokh der milkhome,

00:24:37.992 --> 00:24:39.423
vayl er iz geven

00:24:39.423 --> 00:24:41.293
mit a kepl oyf zikh.

00:24:41.637 --> 00:24:46.440
nor azoy vi er iz nisht gev- g-, aza miesn toyt gegat,

00:24:47.762 --> 00:24:52.093
ho'mir zikh gut ongemutshet nokh der milkhome, un THAT'S ALL.

00:24:52.656 --> 00:24:56.025
ikh hob ersht ongehoybn lebn ven kh'hob khasene gehat far mayn man.

00:24:56.605 --> 00:24:57.746
vos vol-...

00:24:56.655 --> 00:24:58.990
demlt hob ikh ersht ongehoybn lebn.

00:24:59.355 --> 00:25:00.913
vos volt ir veln zogn

00:25:00.913 --> 00:25:03.500
tsu ayere kinder, tsu di eyniklekh,

00:25:03.440 --> 00:25:04.450
tsu di eyniklekh?

00:25:03.642 --> 00:25:06.720
un bikhlal tsu di, tsu di kumedike....?

00:25:04.450 --> 00:25:07.297
ikh, mir redn zeyer oft derfun,

00:25:07.320 --> 00:25:08.979
az zey zoln visn,

00:25:08.979 --> 00:25:11.536
az se kumen di kinder funem kaledzh,

00:25:11.536 --> 00:25:12.731
kumen aheym,

00:25:12.754 --> 00:25:14.269
oyf di ⟨B⟩ACATION,

00:25:14.269 --> 00:25:15.746
zog ikh, "RICHARDl,

00:25:15.746 --> 00:25:17.560
DON'T TAKE a shikse!"

00:25:17.833 --> 00:25:21.860
zogt er, "NO, bobe, ikh gey mit a yidish meydele.

00:25:22.170 --> 00:25:26.450
kh'gey," zogt er, "hob nisht moyre," zogt er. "kh'vel nisht nemen," zogt er, "a shikse."

00:25:26.575 --> 00:25:31.050
zog ikh, "du veyst vi azoy zey hobn getrunken fun undz dos blut,

00:25:31.249 --> 00:25:33.183
vos zey hobn undz geton?

00:25:33.375 --> 00:25:37.250
got zol dikh ophitn! kh'vel dir gibn a gutn PRESENT,

00:25:37.324 --> 00:25:39.624
az du vest mir gibn a PRESENT

00:25:39.624 --> 00:25:41.300
a yidish meydele."

00:25:41.374 --> 00:25:43.070
zogt er, "yo, bobe."

00:25:43.112 --> 00:25:45.792
yetst iz gegan bay der klenerer tokhter

00:25:45.792 --> 00:25:47.412
der zun in kaledzh,

00:25:47.412 --> 00:25:49.270
hob ikh im shoyn gezogt.

00:25:49.270 --> 00:25:50.733
zog ikh, "DANIELe,

00:25:51.313 --> 00:25:57.010
du geyst in kaledzh..." in N.Y.U. kaledzh hot er POSTUPet. er iz zeyer a groyser,

00:25:57.186 --> 00:25:58.952
a kepl a groys...

00:25:59.228 --> 00:26:02.000
zog ikh, "DANIEL." zogt er, "hob nisht moyre, bobe,

00:26:02.000 --> 00:26:05.460
ikh kon geyn mit tsen shikses, nor far zey vel ikh nit khasene hobn."

00:26:07.395 --> 00:26:09.667
dos red ikh tsu mayne kinder,

00:26:09.893 --> 00:26:12.235
zey zoln visn az zey zenen yidn,

00:26:12.235 --> 00:26:14.690
un zoln nemen yidishe kinder.

00:26:15.090 --> 00:26:16.704
kh'hob finef yinglekh.

00:26:17.959 --> 00:26:19.880
zogt mir, far vos hot ir,

00:26:19.880 --> 00:26:25.158
⟨nu⟩, far vos hot ir, vilt ir, hot ir gevelt gebn dem intervyu tsu dem

00:26:26.127 --> 00:26:27.353
FOUNDATION?

00:26:26.194 --> 00:26:28.916
⟨f-⟩ far dem az di kinder

00:26:28.916 --> 00:26:33.010
zoln visn vos di bobe mitn zeydn hot ibergelebt,

00:26:33.010 --> 00:26:35.621
vifl tsores zey zenen durkhgegan.

00:26:35.661 --> 00:26:39.733
ikh denk az mayne tekhter veln es ibermakhn efsher in english.

00:26:39.733 --> 00:26:42.440
tsi s'vet onkumen in english? vi meynt ir?

00:26:42.440 --> 00:26:44.210
s'vet onkumen in yidish?

00:26:44.034 --> 00:26:45.034
⟨ye⟩.

00:26:44.588 --> 00:26:45.949
yo, in yidish?

00:26:46.157 --> 00:26:49.537
mayn tokhter, di groyse, hot gezogt, "MA, du makh es.

00:26:49.537 --> 00:26:51.650
ikh vel es ibermakhn in english.

00:26:51.650 --> 00:26:54.380
ikh vel redn dos alding vos du host geredt,

00:26:54.380 --> 00:26:56.380
un mir vel'mir es makhn in english,

00:26:56.380 --> 00:26:59.290
az tsulib dem az di kinder zoln farshteyn

00:26:59.290 --> 00:27:02.020
un zoln visn vos ir hot ibergelebt.

00:27:02.391 --> 00:27:03.850
a dank aykh.

00:27:03.468 --> 00:27:05.070
nishto far vos.
